div.div:
G: jacobian matrix that describes how the control/odometry ut changes the state from t - 1 to t (denotes the motion model, used to update the covariance matrix P)
R: 3x3 matrix that denotes the noise inherent to the motion estimation
X: estimated state vector (pose and cone positions)
P: state covariance matrix
X and P are used to denote the normal distribution that represents the state
